  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/d170046861fcc01dc3c87803e6ceaceb.avif?t=1761682605\" width=600 height=125 /></span><br><br>Smells Like Burnt Rubber offers intuitive gameplay that lets you jump straight into the action without needing to master complex controls. The game features full controller support, making it easy for anyone to pick up and play.<br><br>Spend your weekend crashing into each other, forgetting the world around you. Neglect your loved ones. You'll never want to drive your own car again—sell it and BUY THIS GAME (twice)!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/55c76ced46c8d81ca19bae8f127ec6c9.poster.avif?t=1761682605\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/55c76ced46c8d81ca19bae8f127ec6c9.webm?t=1761682605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/55c76ced46c8d81ca19bae8f127ec6c9.mp4?t=1761682605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Online Multiplayer</h2>Join online races and compete against players from all around the globe. You can also race locally with friends and have someone join in through online co-op for even more fun!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Up to 4-Player Splitscreen</h2><br>Race against your friends in a couch co-op session with split-screen, whether it’s for a few quick races or the full Grand Prix experience. Smash into your friends' cars and watch them explode as you speed your way to the finish line!<br><br>In local multiplayer, you can use a single keyboard along with as many gamepads as you'd like for a flexible and fun gaming experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/599173694a9aa643e313fa35437d587e.poster.avif?t=1761682605\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/599173694a9aa643e313fa35437d587e.webm?t=1761682605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/599173694a9aa643e313fa35437d587e.mp4?t=1761682605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Global Leaderboard Events</h2><br>There are <strong>monthly</strong> and <strong>weekly</strong> events open to everyone worldwide. You can race as often as you like, and your best time will be recorded. The global leaderboard is visible to all players, allowing you to see your rank in real time against racers from around the world.<br><br>Ask yourself, is anything less than 1st place truly acceptable to you?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/69b8bc7edab694934d234eda519ef7bf.poster.avif?t=1761682605\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/69b8bc7edab694934d234eda519ef7bf.webm?t=1761682605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/69b8bc7edab694934d234eda519ef7bf.mp4?t=1761682605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tracks</h2><br>Race on concrete tracks with high-speed sports cars, or take your monster truck onto mud tracks and shove other drivers into the crash barriers. But be careful! Some tracks have surprises in store — so keep an eye out for oncoming trains!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/060ca8d2f41959797bfb0cfc71a8896b.avif?t=1761682605\" width=616 height=230 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Vehicle Groups</h2><br>Choosing a different vehicle group for each track will reshuffle the deck, completely altering how you handle corners and target collisions with other drivers. You’ll need to adjust your strategy on the fly to come out on top.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/934cdfcfad9715bdd42719971034dba3.poster.avif?t=1761682605\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/934cdfcfad9715bdd42719971034dba3.webm?t=1761682605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenges</h2><br>You can play solo or in local splitscreen with friends across 14 exciting challenges. Think you can beat them all?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/d3581bffd88f654e8297c1bae43c6eab.avif?t=1761682605\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Player customization and Vehicle Tuning</h2><br>Dress your avatar in a variety of colorful suits, and further customize with unique player icons and flags. Craft a look that your friends — or rivals — will come to fear on the track!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/1c44e73738e9f56125bbdbed8fd3d4b9.poster.avif?t=1761682605\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/1c44e73738e9f56125bbdbed8fd3d4b9.webm?t=1761682605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/1c44e73738e9f56125bbdbed8fd3d4b9.mp4?t=1761682605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As you play, you'll earn fame that unlocks new tuning parts, like tires for better grip on various surfaces or chip tuning for enhanced bike performance. You can also take your customization to the next level with vibrant underbody lighting for your vehicles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/e404a87a332f6e5216c8c763dbbaaf32.poster.avif?t=1761682605\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/e404a87a332f6e5216c8c763dbbaaf32.webm?t=1761682605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/e404a87a332f6e5216c8c763dbbaaf32.mp4?t=1761682605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Soundtrack</h2><br>We’re proud to feature a variety of talented German newcomer bands on the game’s soundtrack, adding fresh and exciting music to your racing experience.",
