eamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/060ca8d2f41959797bfb0cfc71a8896b.avif?t=1761682605\" width=616 height=230 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Vehicle Groups</h2><br>Choosing a different vehicle group for each track will reshuffle the deck, completely altering how you handle corners and target collisions with other drivers. You’ll need to adjust your strategy on the fly to come out on top.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/934cdfcfad9715bdd42719971034dba3.poster.avif?t=1761682605\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/934cdfcfad9715bdd42719971034dba3.webm?t=1761682605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenges</h2><br>You can play solo or in local splitscreen with friends across 14 exciting challenges. Think you can beat them all?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/d3581bffd88f654e8297c1bae43c6eab.avif?t=1761682605\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Player customization and Vehicle Tuning</h2><br>Dress your avatar in a variety of colorful suits, and further customize with unique player icons and flags. Craft a look that your friends — or rivals — will come to fear on the track!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/1c44e73738e9f56125bbdbed8fd3d4b9.poster.avif?t=1761682605\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/1c44e73738e9f56125bbdbed8fd3d4b9.webm?t=1761682605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/1c44e73738e9f56125bbdbed8fd3d4b9.mp4?t=1761682605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As you play, you'll earn fame that unlocks new tuning parts, like tires for better grip on various surfaces or chip tuning for enhanced bike performance. You can also take your customization to the next level with vibrant underbody lighting for your vehicles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/e404a87a332f6e5216c8c763dbbaaf32.poster.avif?t=1761682605\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/e404a87a332f6e5216c8c763dbbaaf32.webm?t=1761682605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194840/extras/e404a87a332f6e5216c8c763dbbaaf32.mp4?t=1761682605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Soundtrack</h2><br>We’re proud to feature a variety of talented German newcomer bands on the game’s soundtrack, adding fresh and exciting music to your racing experience.",
